description: Terminal Phase Out management Plan for  CFCs in Implementation of the Montreal Protocol

subproject.description: The TPMP project is aimed at phasing out the use of CFCs in Tanzania. The TPMP investment components have two project components namely: Technical assistance and equipment programme for regional retrofitting centres; and Technical assistance and incentive programme for technology conversions.
subproject.title: TPMP of CFCs-Montreal Protocol

title: Terminal Phase Out Management Plan for Tanzania
